summary: I have a diverse, yet inter-related background and extensive experience in Archaeology, Art, Comparative Religions, Teaching, Research, Writing, Mineral and Gemstones, Antiques, Jewelry, Environmental Protection and Holistic Health. I have followed my passions and expanded on my talents in life and have never regretted it. I have taken the roads less traveled and as they say, it has made all the difference.
